{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862921772,"sessionID":"ses_2865360c9ffeeizJyse5h090bT","part":{"id":"prt_d79ad621e0017gzRrJ62LE93Rw","messageID":"msg_d79ad48320010xfG2Q409lMC3g","sessionID":"ses_2865360c9ffeeizJyse5h090bT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_889ffe7999734b57952283d4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** L  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Prerequisites Validation\n\n- [ ] **T101** Implement `_validate_publish_prerequisites(workspace_path)` in `PublishRuntime`\n  - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` when workspace path does not exist\n  - *Verify:* Raises `FileNotFoundError` when `agent_metadata.yaml` missing\n\n- [ ] **T102** Validate AgentCube provider prerequisites\n  - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` when `provider=\"agentcube\"` and `router_url` missing\n  - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` when `provider=\"agentcube\"` and `workload_manager_url` missing\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Image Preparation\n\n- [ ] **T201** Implement `_prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata)` method\n  - *Verify:* Uses locally built image from metadata when `build_mode=\"local\"`\n\n- [ ] **T202** Implement `_prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata)` method  \n  - *Verify:* Uses cloud registry image URL when `build_mode=\"cloud\"`\n\n- [ ] **T203** Implement image push to registry in `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n  - *Verify:* Pushes image when `image_username` and `image_password` provided\n  - *Verify:* Returns pushed image URL after successful push\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: AgentCube Provider Deployment\n\n- [ ] **T301** Enhance `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` to include CR environment variables\n  - *Verify:* Embeds `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` from metadata\n  - *Verify:* Embeds `ROUTER_URL` from metadata\n  - *Verify:* Sets `sessionTimeout` to `\"15m\"`\n  - *Verify:* Sets `maxSessionDuration` to `\"8h\"`\n  - *Verify:* References `imagePullSecrets` as `[{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]`\n\n- [ ] **T302** Update metadata with AgentRuntime deployment info\n  - *Verify:* Saves `agent_id` to metadata after successful deployment\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Kubernetes Provider Deployment\n\n- [ ] **T401** Implement `wait_for_deployment_ready(namespace, deployment_name, timeout=120)` in `KubernetesProvider`\n  - *Verify:* Waits up to 120 seconds for pods to be ready\n  - *Verify:* Raises `TimeoutError` if timeout exceeded\n\n- [ ] **T402** Update K8s deployment metadata\n  - *Verify:* Saves `k8s_deployment` with: `deployment_name`, `service_name`, `namespace`, `replicas`, `container_port`, `node_port`, `service_url`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Version Handling\n\n- [ ] **T501** Implement version handling logic in `PublishRuntime.publish()`\n  - *Verify:* Uses `--version` from CLI if provided\n  - *Verify:* Falls back to `metadata.version` if CLI version not provided\n  - *Verify:* Defaults to `\"latest\"` if no version in CLI or metadata\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Error Handling\n\n- [ ] **T601** Enhance error messages with verbose logging\n  - *Verify:* Prints full traceback when `--verbose` enabled\n  - *Verify:* Prints error only (no traceback) when `--verbose` disabled\n\n- [ ] **T602** Handle K8s readiness timeout error\n  - *Verify:* Records error in metadata when timeout occurs\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Success Output\n\n- [ ] **T701** Enhance success output with complete deployment details\n  - *Verify:* Displays: Agent name, Provider type (agentcube/k8s), Deployment namespace\n  - *Verify:* Displays: Service URL for K8s or AgentRuntime info for AgentCube\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Testing\n\n- [ ] **T801** Write unit tests for `_validate_publish_prerequisites`\n  - *Verify:* `pytest tests/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"test_validate\"`\n\n- [ ] **T802** Write unit tests for version handling\n  - *Verify:* Tests CLI version, metadata version, and default \"latest\"\n\n- [ ] **T803** Write unit tests for `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n  - *Verify:* Tests local mode, cloud mode, and registry push\n\n- [ ] **T804** Write unit tests for `wait_for_deployment_ready`\n  - *Verify:* Tests timeout behavior\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# CLI help\nkubectl-agentcube publish --help\n\n# Publish to AgentCube (default)\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f /path/to/workspace\n\n# Publish to K8s\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f /path/to/workspace --provider k8s\n\n# Publish with custom version\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f . --version v1.0.0\n\n# Publish with K8s options\nkubectl-agentcube publish -f . --provider k8s --node-port 30001 --replicas 2\n\n# Run publish tests\npytest tests/test_publish_runtime.py -v\n\n# Run lint\nruff check agentcube/\nruff format agentcube/\n\n# Run typecheck\nmypy agentcube/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Requires: AR-021 (build command) completed\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- Uses: `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` (pattern reference)\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria (from delta-spec)\n\n- [ ] AC001: Publish command accepts all specified CLI options\n- [ ] AC002: Publish validates workspace and metadata exist before proceeding\n- [ ] AC003: Publish validates AgentCube prerequisites (router_url, workload_manager_url)\n- [ ] AC004: Publish prepares image for registry (local or cloud mode)\n- [ ] AC005: Publish deploys AgentRuntime CR when provider is \"agentcube\"\n- [ ] AC006: Publish deploys K8s Deployment/Service when provider is \"k8s\"\n- [ ] AC007: Publish waits for K8s deployment readiness (timeout: 120s)\n- [ ] AC008: Publish handles version from CLI, metadata, or default \"latest\"\n- [ ] AC009: Publish updates metadata with deployment information\n- [ ] AC010: Publish displays success output with Rich formatting\n- [ ] AC011: Publish handles errors with appropriate exit codes and verbose logging\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Design stage ST-3 complete - implementation ready\n- Publish supports two providers: \"agentcube\" (AgentRuntime CR) and \"k8s\" (Deployment + NodePort Service)\n- Image push to registry requires `--image-username` and `--image-password`\n- K8s deployment waits up to 120 seconds for pods to become ready","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/cli/main.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775862921741,"end":1775862921769}}}}
